a=A.cX(b3,"Health & Fitness",A.b(["Real-time step counting with Pedometer","Daily activity tracking and statistics","Step history charts using fl_chart","Water intake tracking with daily goals","30+ predefined workouts with timers and measurement","Add custom workouts based on user requirements","Body metrics logging with historical graphs","Daily nutrition tracking with meal logging (breakfast, lunch, dinner, snacks)","Sleep tracking and sleep summary analytics","Burned calories calculation based on workout duration and type","Daily summary of completed workouts and calories burned","Walking/running route tracking on Google Maps","Live location updates","Route polylines using flutter_polyline_points","Distance, speed, and path visualization","Google Places API for location search","Marker clustering for map points","Accurate GPS with Geolocator","Background location support","Live map route drawing","Image picking from camera/gallery","Image cropping and compression","Multiple asset picking (wechat_assets_picker)","Document and file picker support","Cached image handling","Full camera, storage, and location permission handling","Device information collection for analytics","Hive local database","Shared Preferences storage","Offline detection and caching","Dio-powered API communication","Offline-safe requests",d0,"URL launcher integration","Remote Config for dynamic settings",d1,"Local notifications","Multi-language support with easy_localization","Date/number formatting (intl)","Full responsive scaling for all devices","Country picker for onboarding",d2,"Smooth custom loaders","Dotted line UI components","Dropdowns, pin fields","SVG asset rendering","Custom Inter font family","FlutterGen for automatic asset management","Riverpod for structured state management","Freezed models and sealed classes",d3,d4,"Build Runner for automated code generation","Clean, scalable, maintainable codebase"],e9),"A complete fitness, health, and activity tracking application built with Flutter. It features real-time pedometer-based step counting, GPS workout tracking with live polylines, speed/distance stats, and Google Maps integration. Users can track daily workouts, water intake, body metrics, sleep, and nutrition. The app supports 30+ predefined workouts with calorie tracking, history analytics, and custom workout creation. It includes media picking, cropping, compression, offline storage, Firebase notifications, localization, and a fully scalable architecture powered by Riverpod, Freezed, Injectable, Dio, and Hive.",b3,!1,!1,"Developed step tracking, GPS routes, workouts, body metrics, sleep tracking, water intake, and nutrition modules. Implemented maps, media handling, offline storage, Firebase notifications, responsive UI, localization, and scalable architecture using Riverpod, Injectable, Freezed, Dio, and Hive.",A.b([d5,"assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_2.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_3.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_4.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_5.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_6.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_7.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_8.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_9.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_10.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_11.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_12.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_13.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_14.webp","assets/project_mockup/fitme/screen_15.webp"],e9),"Real-time step tracking, GPS routes, workouts, body metrics, water intake, sleep tracking, and full fitness analytics.",a,d5,"Fitness Tracker \u2013 Steps, GPS Routes, Workouts & Activity Monitor")
