a2=A.cX(b3,"Utility",A.b(["Scan QR codes and barcodes","Generate QR codes (text, URL, WiFi, contact, geo)","Generate barcodes in multiple formats","Save, export, and share QR/barcodes","Print QR/barcodes via AirPrint/Google Print","Scan history with local database","Document scanner with camera","Photo selection & cropping","Location-based QR generation","Audio feedback on successful scan","Export as PNG, PDF, CSV, Excel, and ZIP",e0,"Crashlytics error tracking","Firebase Remote Config support","Google Mobile Ads integration",d6,"Responsive UI for phones & tablets"],e9),"A powerful and modern QR/Barcode scanning and generation app built with Flutter. It supports fast scanning, generating multiple QR types (WiFi, contacts, geo, text, URLs), barcode creation, history tracking, and professional export formats like PNG, PDF, CSV, Excel, and ZIP. Includes a document scanner, cropping tools, printing support, localization, responsive UI, and cloud features such as Firebase messaging, Crashlytics, and Remote Config. Fully monetized with Google Ads.",b3,!1,!1,"Implemented fast QR/barcode scanning, developed multi-type QR generator, built export tools (PNG, PDF, CSV, Excel, ZIP), added history with local DB, integrated camera document scanner, and implemented Firebase services with ads.",A.b([e3,"assets/project_mockup/softify_qr/screen_2.webp","assets/project_mockup/softify_qr/screen_3.webp","assets/project_mockup/softify_qr/screen_4.webp","assets/project_mockup/softify_qr/screen_5.webp","assets/project_mockup/softify_qr/screen_6.webp"],e9),"All-in-one QR & barcode scanner and generator with export tools, history, and cloud integrations.",a2,e3,"QR & Barcode Scanner \u2013 Smart Scan & Generator")
